2. cs.RO (Robotics): The paper discusses the motion behaviors of a rigid body, which is a fundamental concept in robotics. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper proposes a descriptor that can learn discriminative motion patterns, which is a machine learning task. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper proposes a descriptor that can recognize different types of rigid body motion, which is an AI task. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia): The paper discusses the application of the proposed descriptor in recognizing human body skeleton motion, which is a multimedia task.
